                                       pmd:symbol "A_g"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/tto/TTO_0000038
<https://w3id.org/pmd/tto/TTO_0000038> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf pmd:PMD_0000848 ,
