                                                       "increase of strain, measured with an extensometer, in extensometer gauge length, per time"@en ;
                                       pmd:definitionSource "DIN EN ISO 6892-1:2019"@en ;
                                       pmd:symbol "e^._L_e"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/tto/TTO_0000052
